text: Introduction .

text: Personal experiences of discrimination and bias have been the focus of much social science research . [ 1 - 3 ]
label: amod nsubj case nmod cc conj aux cop det root case dep amod compound nmod punct punct dep case nmod punct

text: Sociologists have explored the adverse consequences of discrimination [ 3  5 ] ;
label: nsubj aux root det amod obj case nmod punct dep case nmod punct punct

text: psychologists have examined the mental processes that underpin conscious and unconscious biases [ 6 ] ;
label: nsubj aux root det amod obj nsubj acl amod cc conj obj punct dep punct punct

text: neuroscientists have examined the neurobiological underpinnings of discrimination [ 7  9 ] ;
label: nsubj aux root det amod obj case nmod punct dep case nmod punct punct

text: and evolutionary theorists have explored the various ways that in - group / out - group biases emerged across the history of our species . [ 10 ]
label: cc amod nsubj aux root det amod obj mark compound punct compound cc compound punct conj nsubj acl case det obl case nmod nmod punct punct dep punct

text: In many respects , researchers already possess a wealth of knowledge concerning the origins and consequences of discrimination and bias . [ 11 ]
label: case amod obl punct nsubj advmod root det obj case nmod acl det obj cc conj case nmod cc conj punct punct dep punct

text: What also should not be lost in discussion of discrimination is the growing push to implement social policy aimed at reducing the occurrence of discriminatory practices .

text: Mandatory diversity trainings in professional settings , for example , are intended to reduce bias in the workplace by increasing the awareness of employees regarding the challenges facing minority group members . [ 12 ]
label: amod compound nsubj case amod nmod punct case nmod punct aux root mark xcomp obj case det obl mark advcl det obj case nmod case det nmod acl compound compound obj punct punct dep punct

text: Indeed , the implementation of certain policies is rooted in the assumption that discrimination and biases are , at least to some appreciable amount , present in modern society .

text: Even so , estimates of the prevalence of perceived discrimination remains rare ( see [ 13  14 ] ) .

text: At least one prior study by Kessler and colleagues [ 15 ] , however , using measures of perceived discrimination in a large American sample , reported that approximately 33 % of respondents reported some form of discrimination ( see also , Gibbons et al. [ 4 ] ) .
label: advmod fixed nummod amod nsubj case nmod cc conj punct dep punct punct advmod punct acl obj case amod nmod case det amod amod nmod punct root mark advmod nummod nsubj case nmod ccomp det obj case nmod punct parataxis advmod punct obj cc conj punct dep punct punct punct

text: More specifically , when analyzing weighted sample data employing the svy suite of commands in Stata the conventional Pearson 2 statistic test of independence is converted into  an F statistic with noninteger degrees of freedom by using a second - order Rao and Scott ( 1981 [ 22 ] , 1984 [ 23 ] ) correction  . [ 24 ]

text: Antonn Leopold Dvok ( / d()vrk , -k / d()-VOR-zha(h)k ; Czech : [ antoin lopolt dvorak ] ; 8 September 1841  1 May 1904 ) was a Czech composer .

text: Dvok 's own style has been described as " the fullest recreation of a national idiom with that of the symphonic tradition , absorbing folk influences and finding effective ways of using them " . [ 1 ]

text: This is exactly the approach that New Zealand is taking , using three main tools : border controls ; self - isolation ; and good public health practices , including highlighting the importance of basic hygiene .

text: Of course , members will be aware that there are outbreaks in other regions as well .

text: So , as a further precaution , we have decided that anyone arriving in New Zealand who has been in northern Italy or South Korea who has been there in the last 14 days will be registered for self - isolation .

label: nsubj root mark mark expl advcl nsubj case det obl punct nsubj advmod ccomp advmod punct amod compound obj cc det nsubj aux advmod conj case amod obl punct

text: We know self - isolation works .
label: nsubj root compound punct nsubj ccomp punct

text: We have also stepped up the health presence at our airports .

text: 2.1 Early Ideas in Atomic Theory
label: dep amod root case amod nmod

text: By the end of this section , you will be able to :
label: case det obl case det nmod punct nsubj aux cop root xcomp punct

text: State the postulates of Dalton s atomic theory
label: root det obj case nmod case amod nmod

text: Use postulates of Dalton s atomic theory to explain the laws of definite and multiple proportions
label: root obj case nmod case amod nmod mark advcl det obj case amod cc conj nmod

text: The earliest recorded discussion of the basic structure of matter comes from ancient Greek philosophers , the scientists of their day .
label: det amod amod nsubj case det amod nmod case nmod root case amod amod obl punct det appos case nmod nmod punct

text: In the fifth century BC , Leucippus and Democritus argued that all matter was composed of small , finite particles that they called atomos , a term derived from the Greek word for  indivisible .
label: case det amod obl advmod punct nsubj cc conj root mark det nsubj aux ccomp case amod punct amod obl obj nsubj acl xcomp punct det appos acl case det amod obl case punct nmod punct punct

text: They thought of atoms as moving particles that differed in shape and size , and which could join together .
label: nsubj root case obl case amod obl nsubj acl case obl cc conj punct cc nsubj aux conj advmod punct

text: Later , Aristotle and others came to the conclusion that matter consisted of various combinations of the four  elements   fire , earth , air , and water  and could be infinitely divided .

text: Interestingly , these philosophers thought about atoms and  elements  as philosophical concepts , but apparently never considered performing experiments to test their ideas .

text: Method 2 of 2 : From Cuttings

text: Choose a spot for your Beavertail cactus cuttings .

text: How to Get Rid of Mice Naturally
label: root mark acl xcomp case obl advmod

text: Having mice in your home is both a nuisance and a health hazard .
label: csubj obj case nmod nmod cop cc det root cc det compound conj punct

text: They can cause property damage , create a mess , and produce unpleasant smells .
label: nsubj aux root compound obj punct conj det obj punct cc conj amod obj punct

text: In addition , repelling and removing rodents from your home can be a hassle if you do n't know what you are doing .
label: case nmod punct csubj cc conj obj case nmod obl aux cop det root mark nsubj aux advmod advcl obj nsubj aux acl punct

text: It can also be dangerous if you use toxic chemicals and poisons .
label: nsubj aux advmod cop root mark nsubj advcl amod obj cc conj punct

text: It 's a good thing , then , that there are some simple ways to effectively get mice out of your home without the use of toxic chemicals and poisons .
label: expl cop det amod root punct advmod punct mark expl csubj det amod nsubj mark advmod acl obj case fixed nmod obl case det obl case amod nmod cc conj punct

text: Method 1 Discouraging Mice Naturally
label: root dep appos obj advmod

text: Keep your home clean .
label: root nmod obj xcomp punct

text: Many times mice are drawn into homes on the search for food .
label: amod obl nsubj aux root case obl case det nmod case nmod punct

text: If there is nothing to eat , mice will be less likely to stay .
label: mark expl advcl nsubj mark acl punct nsubj aux cop advmod root mark xcomp punct

text: Keep all food stored properly in airtight containers or in places that are safe from mouse attack . [ 1 ]
label: root det obj xcomp advmod case amod obl cc case conj nsubj cop acl case compound obl punct punct dep punct

text: Apply peppermint oil .
label: root compound obj punct

text: Peppermint oil is a natural deterrent .
label: compound nsubj cop det amod root punct

text: The smell is simply too intense for rodents and they will not try to go near it .
label: det nsubj cop advmod advmod root case obl cc nsubj aux advmod conj mark xcomp case obl punct

text: It also helps to mask the scent of any tasty morsels that have been missed when cleaning .
label: nsubj advmod root mark xcomp det obj case det amod nmod nsubj aux aux acl advmod advcl punct

text: It also gives the house a lovely smell , and is not toxic , unlike many synthetic chemical treatments .
label: nsubj advmod root det iobj det amod obj punct cc cop advmod conj punct case amod amod compound conj punct

text: You can get peppermint oil in most health food stores and even some major grocery stores . [ 2 ]
label: nsubj aux root compound obj case amod compound compound obl cc advmod det amod compound conj punct punct dep punct

text: Place a drop or two on a cotton ball .
label: root det obj cc conj case det compound obl punct

text: Place a cotton ball under or near your garbage can to deter mice from getting into it .
label: root det compound obj case cc conj nmod compound obl mark advcl obj mark advcl case obl punct

text: Place the cotton balls in areas where mice are likely to enter your house , by doorways , or heat vents , etc.
label: root det compound obj case obl advmod nsubj cop advcl mark xcomp nmod obj punct case obl punct cc compound conj punct conj

text: Peppermint oil cotton balls need to be replaced after 5 - 7 days , depending upon the quantity of oil you put on it .
label: compound compound compound nsubj root mark aux xcomp case nummod case nmod obl punct case fixed det obl case nmod nsubj parataxis case obl punct

text: Try growing peppermint plants near the entryways .
label: root xcomp compound obj case det obl punct

text: You can use the mint in cooking , as well as it serving a deterrent purpose .
label: nsubj aux root det obj case obl punct cc fixed fixed nsubj conj det compound obj punct

text: Use dried snake feces .
label: root amod compound obj punct

text: Visit a local reptile center , zoo , or pet store and ask for some dried snake poo .
label: root det amod compound obj punct conj punct cc compound conj cc conj case det amod compound obl punct

text: You can also sometimes find someone who owns a pet snake .
label: nsubj aux advmod advmod root obj nsubj acl det compound obj punct

text: Place near entrances and in places where mice seem to go .
label: root case obl cc case conj advmod nsubj acl mark xcomp punct

text: This will keep mice away . [ 3 ]
label: nsubj aux root obj advmod punct punct dep punct

text: Be sure to keep the feces out of the reach of children and pets .
label: cop root mark xcomp det obj case fixed det obl case nmod cc conj punct

text: Zap mice with ultrasonic sounds .
label: root obj case amod obl punct

text: There are electronic units sold that emit an ultrasonic beeping sound that rodents hate .
label: expl root amod nsubj acl nsubj acl det amod compound obj obj nsubj acl punct

text: They should be available at your local home improvement store or online .
label: nsubj aux cop root case nmod amod compound compound obl cc conj punct

text: These work only on a single line of sight , so you need to know the exact path the mice are taking .
label: nsubj root advmod case det amod obl case nmod punct advmod nsubj parataxis mark xcomp det amod obj det nsubj aux acl punct

text: The units may only work for a short time because mice can become used to them . [ 4 ]
label: det nsubj aux advmod root case det amod obl mark nsubj aux advcl xcomp case obl punct punct dep punct

text: Use a commercial , organic deterrent .
label: root det amod punct amod obj punct

text: Many companies that specialize in organic garden and home products make mice repellents that are better for the environment than traditional poisons .
label: amod nsubj nsubj acl case amod obl cc compound conj root compound obj nsubj cop acl case det obl case amod obl punct

text: Many of these products use natural ingredients , such as peppermint , that are known to be disagreeable to mice .

text: They will not kill mice but they should keep them out of areas where the product is applied .

text: These products should be available at your local gardening or home improvement center .

text: If you want a specific product , try doing a online search to see where it is available locally .

text: Get a cat .

text: A house cat can take care of the problem .

text: Cats that spend time outdoors are more likely to hunt to find their own food and may track down that mouse .

text: Just be aware , not all cats have enough energy , interest or training to hunt mice .

text: Kittens typically have to be taught by the mother to easily become a mouser .

text: Well - food indoor kitties might just see the mouse as a toy , and grow quickly bored of it after scaring it half witless .

text: Shelters and adoption agencies often do not know if a cat is a good mouse hunter , and generally do not test for this .

text: While many mousers are great pets as well , not all are .

text: " Barn cats " may not be socialized well with humans , although used to hunting mice for food .

text: Even if you do not have a cat , you can use used kitty litter to deter mice .

text: Place tubs of used kitty litter around entrances of the house .

text: However , once you eliminate the infestation , a cat will probably prevent reinfestation . [ 5 ]

text: Put your trash cans far from your home .
